{{> header subject="Password Changed Successfully"}}

<h2 style="margin: 0 0 20px; color: #333; font-size: 24px;">Password Changed</h2>

<p style="margin: 0 0 20px;">Hi {{name}},</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 20px;">Your Dhanam account password was successfully changed on {{changedAt}}.</p>

<div style="margin: 30px 0; padding: 20px; background-color: #f5f5f5; border-radius: 4px;">
  <p style="margin: 0 0 10px; font-weight: 600;">Was this you?</p>
  <p style="margin: 0;">If you made this change, no further action is needed. Your account is secure.</p>
</div>

<div style="margin: 30px 0; padding: 20px; background-color: #fee; border-radius: 4px; border-left: 4px solid #f44336;">
  <p style="margin: 0 0 10px; font-weight: 600; color: #d32f2f;">Didn't change your password?</p>
  <p style="margin: 0 0 15px;">If you didn't make this change, your account may be compromised. Take these steps immediately:</p>
  <ol style="margin: 0; padding-left: 20px;">
    <li>Reset your password using the link below</li>
    <li>Enable two-factor authentication</li>
    <li>Review your recent account activity</li>
    <li>Contact our support team</li>
  </ol>
</div>

{{> button text="Secure My Account" url=(concat appUrl "/security") buttonColor="#f44336"}}

<p style="margin: 0;">Stay safe,<br>The Dhanam Security Team</p>

{{> footer}}